I"á<h4 id="jekyll-3-install">Jekyll 3 Install</h4>
<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">gem install jekyll</code></p>

<p>note: if this returns that it <code class="highlighter-rouge">requires &gt; ruby 2.0.11</code> then 
<code class="highlighter-rouge">rvm install ruby-[latest]</code></p>

<h4 id="changes-to-make-hyde-theme-compatible-with-jekyll-3">Changes to make Hyde theme compatible with jekyll 3</h4>
<ol>
  <li>
    <p>_config.yml</p>

    <ul>
      <li>add line: <code class="highlighter-rouge">paginate_path: "page:num"</code></li>
      <li>add line: <code class="highlighter-rouge">plugins: [jekyll-paginate, jeyll-gist]</code></li>
      <li>remove line: <code class="highlighter-rouge">relative_permalinks: true</code></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><code class="highlighter-rouge">gem install jekyll-paginate redcarpet jekyll-gist</code></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><code class="highlighter-rouge">jekyll serve &amp;&amp; open http://127.0.0.1:4000</code></p>
  </li>
</ol>

